line-height: 2em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><img alt=\"Vận chuyển nhanh chóng, đúng hẹn\" height=\"467\" src=\"https://sudospaces.com/labvietchem-com-vn/2019/01/chinh-sach-labvietchem-2-1.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: block;\" width=\"700\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt;\">Vận chuyển nhanh ch&oacute;ng, đ&uacute;ng hẹn</em></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><img alt=\"Nhân viên giao nhận nhiệt tình, chu đáo\" height=\"467\" src=\"https://sudospaces.com/labvietchem-com-vn/2019/01/chinh-sach-labvietchem-1-1.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: block;\" width=\"700\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; marg